ment in this conversation in an open Google Group <ns7:ext-link xmlns:ns8="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" ext-link-type="uri" ns8:href="mailto:fair-assessment-governance@googlegroups.com">fair-assessment-governance@googlegroups.com</ns7:ext-link></ns7:p>
