enting with alternative methods of evaluating research such as Altmetric and the SCImago Journal &amp; Country Rank. I will conclude with an overview of how we are working with research organisations and universities to offer financial support to their researchers in order to cover the fee for publishing in BioMed Central and SpringerOpen journals in the context of our institutional membership program.
