.Ononogbo (2003) discovered that 91 percent of the collection in the library being studied was derived from donations, gifts, and bequests.A collection development policy is therefore needed that delineates the purpose and contents of a collection relevant to its users as a whole (Evans, 2000; Futas, 1984)
